{"tid":1325601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛分化post蠢蠢欲動","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:27:09.000Z","uid":50457,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cf9e49bc365ca1d60d0759cb9ca96fed8674f8","tid":1325601,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:33:34.000Z","msg":"五毛每兩，三日都會帶一次風向<br />\n<br />\n主要為：<br />\n1. 泛民同示威者分化post,  因為如果無左泛民議員係前線，示威者頓失大量緩衝空間同法律支援<br />\n2. 中國出軍隊，軍演post,  一味靠嚇<br />\n3. 政府跪低post,  搏大家同情<br />\n4. 有良心克警post,   搏大家同情<br />\n5. 聽朋友講關於&ldquo;鬧示威者&rdquo;post,  扮哂朋友就企係正義立場，令人產生示威者係邪惡的定性<br />\n6. 挑釁post,  推一啲無關重要的小人朋鬧示威者post,  令大家花時間將憤怒轉移到呢班小人物身上（如某中學教師，某警察家屬，某youtuber,  某機構人員）最近主力<br />\n7. 垃圾post,  推舊新聞，得標題的post,  目的推走有用的資訊post<br />\n8. 散播失敗論，做乜都無用的post,  目的打擊大家行動的動力<br />\n<br />\n一直推post直到7。21<br />\n<br />\n記緊！！！警惕每一個回覆，積極回應五毛post係佢地最想的<br />\n<br />\n大家要沉住氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不回覆，不分化"},{"pid":"29629ad9284f37619bc354d854d8ea98c7409a48","tid":1325601,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddba4ec1fd02633e65a520cdd0fc08ef0afdc44","tid":1325601,"uid":280436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"5913f908681c0fdef42f8fb6ce2450ee9c12cc30","tid":1325601,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11b309787bf3fa3219b09db5bae7444df9f0450","tid":1325601,"uid":62776,